room_title: Escape room "The Bunker" by Escapeburg in New York
review: We recently tried out Putin's bunker which was great fun! There were 4 of us who went and everyone had a great time. I personally felt the ending was a bit weak but the concept in the beginning is unique and interesting :) Everyone check them out!

room_title: Escape room "The Bunker" by Escapeburg in New York
review: This place is awesome. I tried the Bunker with only 2 people. In the beginning I was scared. Tied up to a chair, just awesome. Looking forward to go to the new escape rooms.

room_title: Escape room "The Bunker" by Escapeburg in New York
review: I tried bunker and im going to go back with my friends for tomb ASAP it was amazingly fun!
